metadata.name: Walk  in  BLeU
metadata.description:
"Sometime we walk alone to know what it takes to be victorious not in just the path we take for our goals but in life for all little details we ignored"  -sigmax


My tribute to @0xTjo CCO released artwork.
Combining my Grail of Minimalism

Artist:   Tjo  & Sigmax

Edition: 1/1

License: CCO
Permission granted by artist of BLeU (Tjo)

This work would help me raise fund for my master program at Architectural Association , London 
Masters in Sustainability.
Be a part of historic movement in art renaissance
